WEBVTT

01:37.080 --> 01:40.979
[The Best Thing]

01:41.310 --> 01:48.229
[Episode 26: Poria]
[Sweet and bland in taste, neutral in nature, promotes urination and drains dampness, strengthens the spleen, calms the mind.]

02:51.160 --> 02:52.230
You're back.

02:55.000 --> 02:55.950
What time is it now?

02:58.980 --> 02:59.930
Six o'clock.

03:01.720 --> 03:04.120
Why did you come back later than me today?

03:09.440 --> 03:10.790
I was busy with some other things.

03:23.880 --> 03:24.600
Are you hungry?

03:27.390 --> 03:28.790
I'll go make dinner for you.

03:32.000 --> 03:33.230
Let's eat out.

03:34.920 --> 03:35.320
Okay.

03:36.280 --> 03:36.670
Let's go.

03:38.970 --> 03:39.570
Hug.

05:07.490 --> 05:08.890
[Best Employee of the Year: Shen Xifan]

05:46.040 --> 05:47.640
The interview is over.

05:47.640 --> 05:49.960
I'll just wait for the result.

05:59.550 --> 06:01.400
This place is quite close to He Suye's hospital,

06:01.400 --> 06:03.080
isn't it?

06:03.990 --> 06:06.520
Congratulations on completing a big task, Ms. Shen.

06:06.790 --> 06:08.750
We'll celebrate with you when we get back tonight.

06:20.230 --> 06:20.960
This arm.

06:23.270 --> 06:23.830
Hold on.

06:23.870 --> 06:24.670
Be careful.

06:24.950 --> 06:25.730
Are you alright?

06:31.640 --> 06:32.670
Let me tie it for you.

06:32.670 --> 06:33.740
I can do it myself.

06:39.110 --> 06:40.080
Dr. He. Here.

06:41.350 --> 06:42.080
Look.

06:42.230 --> 06:42.870
This drainage bag.

06:42.870 --> 06:43.920
It's not visible anymore, is it?

06:43.920 --> 06:44.790
It's not.

06:45.840 --> 06:46.990
It's good that it's not visible.

06:47.159 --> 06:48.640
This way, Ms. Shen won't find out about it.

06:48.640 --> 06:49.230
Right.

06:50.960 --> 06:51.790
He.

06:53.080 --> 06:54.670
How many more days do I have to wear this?

06:55.800 --> 06:56.770
A week.

06:59.230 --> 07:02.670
Then take Ms. Shen out more this week.

07:03.670 --> 07:05.750
I'm worried she'll be scared if she finds out.

07:05.920 --> 07:06.520
Yes.

07:12.190 --> 07:12.990
Mrs. Shen.

07:13.550 --> 07:15.920
When are you going to tell Xifan?

07:17.520 --> 07:18.930
After the test results come out.

07:20.670 --> 07:21.620
You mean the pathology report?

07:24.980 --> 07:26.650
Everything will be certain by then.

07:28.160 --> 07:29.080
Then I'll tell her.

07:33.080 --> 07:33.690
Okay.

07:34.670 --> 07:36.550
I'll pick it up for you then.

07:36.640 --> 07:37.890
So you don't have to make another run.

07:37.990 --> 07:38.870
Thank you.

07:38.870 --> 07:39.550
It's nothing.

07:40.750 --> 07:41.350
Come on. Be careful.

07:41.350 --> 07:41.870
It's okay.

07:41.870 --> 07:42.330
Take it slow.

07:42.350 --> 07:43.230
It's okay, it's okay.

07:44.750 --> 07:46.990
I've caused you a lot of trouble these days.

07:46.990 --> 07:47.920
Thank you for everything.

07:47.920 --> 07:48.550
It's no trouble.

07:48.550 --> 07:49.680
I just did what I should.

07:50.350 --> 07:52.080
After you get home, make sure to rest well

07:52.080 --> 07:53.110
and take your medicine on time.

07:53.430 --> 07:55.560
Leave the rest to me.

07:55.640 --> 07:56.550
Okay.

07:58.110 --> 07:58.960
I'll see you out then.

08:01.730 --> 08:02.340
Be careful.

08:22.110 --> 08:23.640
He, you can stop here.

08:23.640 --> 08:24.920
You should get back to work.

08:24.920 --> 08:25.960
We'll see ourselves out.

08:28.310 --> 08:28.840
Give me the bags.

08:28.980 --> 08:29.580
Okay.

08:30.640 --> 08:32.000
If you feel any discomfort, Mrs. Shen,

08:32.000 --> 08:32.880
let me know immediately.

08:33.140 --> 08:34.020
Thank you for your trouble.

08:34.230 --> 08:35.070
It's no problem.

08:37.470 --> 08:38.549
By the way, Ms. Shen,

08:39.520 --> 08:40.470
Your mother's company arranged for

08:40.470 --> 08:42.590
a training in the neighboring city tomorrow.

08:43.370 --> 08:44.770
I rescheduled my classes for two days

08:45.210 --> 08:47.090
so that I could go with her.

08:48.950 --> 08:50.520
Thank you. We'll be leaving now.

08:50.520 --> 08:51.280
Bye-bye.

08:51.430 --> 08:52.040
Take it slow.

09:06.520 --> 09:08.790
I'm at the hospital. Let's meet.

09:46.420 --> 09:47.830
Are the physical examination results out?

09:48.760 --> 09:50.120
It's not that fast.

09:52.400 --> 09:55.050
But the doctor said everything looks healthy.

10:02.870 --> 10:03.750
He Suye.

10:09.220 --> 10:10.100
He Suye.

10:10.400 --> 10:11.160
What's wrong?

10:12.000 --> 10:12.670
It's nothing.

11:09.040 --> 11:10.040
Why are you here?

11:13.280 --> 11:14.830
I was applying for my visa nearby.

11:15.810 --> 11:17.510
I realized it's quite close to the hospital,

11:18.360 --> 11:19.690
so I came to wait for you to get off work.

11:37.430 --> 11:38.160
My mom...

11:38.990 --> 11:40.110
Is she sick?

11:44.340 --> 11:44.890
Yes.

11:45.460 --> 11:46.460
What's her disease?

11:52.520 --> 11:53.360
Breast cancer.

11:58.240 --> 11:59.280
Breast tumor.

12:00.550 --> 12:01.400
Malignant.

12:12.710 --> 12:14.110
When did they find out?

12:16.950 --> 12:17.880
Four days ago.

12:19.810 --> 12:21.330
So they lied to me about going on a business trip

12:23.640 --> 12:25.190
when they actually came to the hospital.

12:31.770 --> 12:33.050
What stage is her cancer at now?

12:34.550 --> 12:36.240
The removal surgery has been done.

12:37.190 --> 12:37.920
When...

12:38.190 --> 12:39.640
When the pathology report comes out,

12:39.790 --> 12:41.670
we'll arrange the treatment plan.

12:48.360 --> 12:49.190
This.

12:50.470 --> 12:53.000
This is the result of the intraoperative rapid pathology.

12:53.310 --> 12:54.400
The tumor is not big,

12:54.400 --> 12:57.040
and there's no sign of metastasis or spread for now.

12:57.310 --> 12:59.040
Actually, the situation is quite optimistic.

12:59.120 --> 12:59.940
-Don't worry.
-So…

13:00.540 --> 13:01.970
So is my mom okay now?

13:02.920 --> 13:04.430
Does she still need to do chemo?

13:05.760 --> 13:06.850
It's such a big deal.

13:07.830 --> 13:08.430
You...

13:08.640 --> 13:10.120
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

13:12.920 --> 13:14.430
Before the removal surgery,

13:14.830 --> 13:17.070
we couldn't be sure if it was a malignant tumor.

13:18.160 --> 13:19.520
We didn't want you to be worried,

13:19.520 --> 13:20.070
so...

13:20.100 --> 13:21.680
But she's my mother!

13:22.830 --> 13:25.310
Do you know how scared I was just now?

13:26.590 --> 13:27.770
I'm scared of accidents.

13:29.980 --> 13:32.060
I'm scared of all the accidents in this world,

13:32.080 --> 13:33.080
He Suye.

13:44.920 --> 13:45.590
I'm sorry.

13:46.470 --> 13:47.380
I...

13:47.950 --> 13:49.280
I didn't think it through.

13:52.240 --> 13:52.950
But I...

14:17.710 --> 14:19.240
He, wanna have lunch together?

14:26.560 --> 14:27.990
What's wrong with him?

14:51.360 --> 14:52.970
But she's my mother!

14:54.100 --> 14:56.570
Do you know how scared I was just now?

14:57.920 --> 14:59.160
I'm scared of accidents.

15:01.160 --> 15:03.400
I'm scared of all the accidents in this world,

15:03.400 --> 15:04.710
He Suye.

16:17.990 --> 16:20.390
[Shen Xifan]

16:52.070 --> 16:57.110
[Xu Xiangya]

17:00.830 --> 17:01.760
Hello, Xiangya.

17:02.590 --> 17:05.560
Well, do you know where Xifan is now?

17:06.190 --> 17:07.160
She's with me.

17:19.839 --> 17:21.359
You should trust Dr. He.

17:21.599 --> 17:22.880
He's a professional.

17:23.880 --> 17:25.800
Since he said your mom's tumor isn't serious

17:25.800 --> 17:26.819
and there shouldn't be a problem,

17:26.950 --> 17:28.270
it must be reliable.

17:30.360 --> 17:31.430
Don't worry too much.

17:35.990 --> 17:37.510
What are your plans now?

17:41.080 --> 17:43.500
I'll leave the professional matters to He Suye.

17:44.270 --> 17:45.910
I'll go home and spend more time with my mom.

17:46.420 --> 17:48.350
I'll talk to him tonight.

17:50.470 --> 17:52.670
The timing is good. You've just completed your resignation process,

17:52.670 --> 17:53.920
so you can focus on keeping your mom company.

18:05.160 --> 18:06.120
Have a good chat, Sweetie.

18:39.850 --> 18:41.660
Mrs. Shen had previously asked me

18:44.120 --> 18:46.190
to not tell you anything until the pathology report

18:47.320 --> 18:48.470
came out.

18:51.670 --> 18:53.080
As a doctor,

18:54.990 --> 18:56.950
I have the responsibility to keep my patients' information confidential.

18:58.420 --> 19:00.130
This is also out of respect for Mrs. Shen.

19:08.160 --> 19:09.680
But what you said is also right.

19:11.990 --> 19:13.920
I've experienced my mom's battle with cancer and her passing.

19:14.030 --> 19:15.430
I know how lost the patients' children can be

19:16.690 --> 19:18.130
at a time like this.

19:19.990 --> 19:21.600
Even though there was nothing I could do,

19:22.990 --> 19:24.560
I still rushed to the hospital

19:26.320 --> 19:27.670
as soon as school was over every day,

19:30.640 --> 19:32.360
fearing I might suddenly lose her.

19:42.360 --> 19:43.320
So,

19:46.080 --> 19:48.030
it's my fault for not taking good care of your feelings.

19:50.060 --> 19:51.150
I'm sorry.

19:56.870 --> 19:58.000
I'm also at fault.

19:59.230 --> 20:00.990
I got too emotional at the time,

20:01.950 --> 20:04.080
and I said so many harsh things.

20:05.090 --> 20:06.090
He Suye.

20:08.270 --> 20:09.880
I didn't do it on purpose.

20:11.510 --> 20:12.670
I'm sorry.

20:14.750 --> 20:15.750
It's okay.

20:18.560 --> 20:19.750
Mrs. Shen will be fine.

20:22.190 --> 20:23.710
Both of you are my family,

20:24.230 --> 20:25.510
and also my responsibility.

20:27.120 --> 20:29.120
I'll definitely take good care of Mrs. Shen.

20:34.950 --> 20:35.670
It's alright now.

20:41.950 --> 20:42.920
I'm sorry.

21:11.670 --> 21:12.460
Be careful.

21:24.920 --> 21:27.640
Don't worry. Everything will be okay.

21:28.670 --> 21:29.860
Mrs. Shen's condition

21:29.950 --> 21:31.160
is quite optimistic.

21:31.430 --> 21:32.560
When you get home,

21:32.560 --> 21:34.400
tell Mr. and Mrs. Shen to relax.

21:34.560 --> 21:35.560
Everything will be okay.

21:38.880 --> 21:39.830
I'll go up now.

21:46.030 --> 21:46.750
It's okay.

21:47.080 --> 21:47.840
Don't overthink it.

21:53.600 --> 21:54.360
I'll be going then.

21:54.640 --> 21:55.320
Go ahead.

21:55.990 --> 21:56.600
Good night.

21:56.630 --> 21:57.230
Good night.

22:26.520 --> 22:27.600
Let me try it.

22:29.950 --> 22:30.840
Is it drinkable now?

22:31.800 --> 22:32.680
The temperature is perfect.

22:35.750 --> 22:36.800
Come on, help me up.

22:36.800 --> 22:37.400
Can you do it?

22:37.670 --> 22:38.270
Help me up.

22:38.300 --> 22:39.150
Be careful.

22:41.400 --> 22:42.510
Quick, hide it.

22:51.360 --> 22:52.270
I'm back.

22:54.360 --> 22:55.730
Why are you back so late?

22:55.840 --> 22:57.120
You went on a date with He?

22:59.060 --> 22:59.740
Yes, I did.

23:08.360 --> 23:10.160
Take your medicine. It's getting cold.

23:13.710 --> 23:14.430
At least there's...

23:14.430 --> 23:15.140
I'll drink it.

23:15.250 --> 23:17.520
Alright, put it down.

23:17.840 --> 23:19.030
This isn't even your medicine.

23:20.640 --> 23:21.430
It...

23:21.430 --> 23:22.560
It's my medicine.

23:22.560 --> 23:23.430
What's wrong with you?

23:23.430 --> 23:24.160
You must have taken the wrong one.

23:24.160 --> 23:26.560
This is... This is my medicine.

23:26.560 --> 23:27.120
It's just...

23:27.120 --> 23:30.400
I went to the hospital today to see He Suye,

23:30.400 --> 23:31.470
and I saw you two.

23:33.740 --> 23:34.710
Ah, you...

23:35.670 --> 23:36.690
So you know?

23:39.320 --> 23:41.560
He Suye told me that

23:41.560 --> 23:42.610
your condition is quite optimistic.

23:43.080 --> 23:45.160
Just leave the professional matters to him.

23:45.200 --> 23:46.920
Let's just cooperate, okay?

23:53.560 --> 23:54.640
It's alright.

23:55.930 --> 23:57.000
You've had the surgery?

24:00.270 --> 24:01.520
Does the wound hurt?

24:02.120 --> 24:03.320
It doesn't.

24:03.950 --> 24:05.280
Not even a bit.

24:06.030 --> 24:06.950
Where is it?

24:07.430 --> 24:08.040
It's right here.

24:08.600 --> 24:09.640
It's in here.

24:09.640 --> 24:10.950
You can't even see it.

24:34.880 --> 24:36.240
A drainage bag?

24:39.360 --> 24:41.710
He said wearing this drainage bag

24:41.710 --> 24:44.360
is to prevent fluid accumulation and infection.

24:44.360 --> 24:45.360
Yes, right.

24:45.950 --> 24:48.360
It helps the wound heal faster.

24:50.000 --> 24:51.280
As long as it heals fast.

24:52.990 --> 24:54.030
It's okay.

24:56.780 --> 24:57.820
Take your medicine.

24:57.990 --> 24:58.920
Right.

24:59.160 --> 25:00.400
Or it'll get cold.

25:01.920 --> 25:02.670
Be careful.

25:06.510 --> 25:07.400
It must be bitter.

25:11.600 --> 25:13.100
-Take it slow.
-Slowly.

25:14.670 --> 25:16.040
It's really bitter.

25:21.880 --> 25:23.640
No wonder you were unwilling to drink it before.

25:38.030 --> 25:39.510
Let me check your tongue coating.

25:41.990 --> 25:42.880
Good, good.

25:43.190 --> 25:44.160
It looks good.

25:46.670 --> 25:49.150
Do you have the prescription that Suye gave you last time?

25:49.880 --> 25:51.560
Yes, it's in my phone.

25:52.750 --> 25:53.640
Look.

25:53.730 --> 25:54.250
Okay.

25:54.280 --> 25:55.280
Let me see.

25:58.430 --> 25:59.080
Not bad.

25:59.990 --> 26:01.160
It promotes blood circulation, relieves pain,

26:01.710 --> 26:02.880
replenishes qi, and nourishes blood.

26:03.800 --> 26:05.470
Take the medicine on time every day.

26:05.670 --> 26:08.080
Move around when you're feeling well.

26:08.080 --> 26:10.360
Keep your spirits up.

26:11.030 --> 26:13.120
That should be good.

26:13.520 --> 26:14.080
Okay.

26:14.120 --> 26:14.800
There's no problem.

26:14.800 --> 26:17.080
It's fine. Don't be nervous.

26:18.120 --> 26:19.430
I understand.

26:19.690 --> 26:22.780
This period of waiting for the pathology results

26:22.800 --> 26:24.080
is always agonizing.

26:25.640 --> 26:27.230
Don't worry.

26:27.560 --> 26:28.920
With Suye and I here,

26:29.360 --> 26:31.400
you'll definitely get through this tough time.

26:32.950 --> 26:35.190
Thank you, and thank you to Suye as well.

26:35.450 --> 26:37.130
Please, don't mention it.

26:39.510 --> 26:40.600
My daughter is gone.

26:40.600 --> 26:43.230
Now my grandson, Suye, is the only family

26:43.230 --> 26:43.990
by my side.

26:44.880 --> 26:48.190
Since fate brought him and Shen together,

26:48.670 --> 26:49.840
I should see you

26:49.870 --> 26:52.460
as my family.

26:52.990 --> 26:53.600
Of course,

26:53.600 --> 26:54.470
As a family,

26:54.470 --> 26:56.030
we're supposed to take care of each other

26:56.030 --> 26:57.400
and share each other's burdens.

27:01.160 --> 27:01.950
I

27:01.950 --> 27:03.840
will teach you a few moves

27:04.750 --> 27:05.920
that can not only

27:06.640 --> 27:08.120
strengthen your body,

27:08.120 --> 27:09.670
but also help dispel stagnant energy

27:09.670 --> 27:10.470
and relieve stress.

27:10.470 --> 27:11.470
Okay. Okay.

27:12.510 --> 27:13.430
Can you get up?

27:16.260 --> 27:18.460
Mr. Shen, this is mainly for you to learn.

27:18.480 --> 27:19.740
Once you learn it well,

27:19.840 --> 27:21.190
you can teach Ms. Liu.

27:21.190 --> 27:22.190
Alright, alright.

27:24.670 --> 27:25.880
Cross your hands.

27:25.880 --> 27:26.710
Cross them.

27:27.190 --> 27:29.180
Place them in front of the Danzhong acupoint.

27:29.210 --> 27:30.020
Danzhong?

27:30.040 --> 27:32.630
The Danzhong acupoint is between the breasts.

27:33.520 --> 27:34.390
That's right.

27:36.280 --> 27:37.430
Flip your wrists

27:37.800 --> 27:41.430
back and forth to tap the Danzhong acupoint.

27:41.970 --> 27:42.840
Look.

27:44.860 --> 27:45.740
Slower.

27:52.200 --> 27:52.670
It's okay.

27:52.670 --> 27:54.120
See, you're using too much force.

27:54.990 --> 27:55.510
It hurts a bit.

27:55.510 --> 27:57.160
50 times a set.

27:58.250 --> 28:00.050
It can help dispel stagnant energy and relieve stress.

28:13.880 --> 28:15.400
I want to study abroad

28:15.400 --> 28:16.320
in Switzerland

28:16.990 --> 28:18.400
for a master's degree in hotel management.

28:18.950 --> 28:21.080
I want to go out and see the world,

28:21.080 --> 28:22.670
and further my studies abroad.

28:22.670 --> 28:25.030
I think you should go out and explore the world.

28:25.470 --> 28:26.990
What if it turns out to be everything you hoped for?

28:28.230 --> 28:29.320
This time, I plan to

28:29.320 --> 28:31.160
apply to the top three universities in the world.

28:31.560 --> 28:32.490
It's very challenging,

28:32.600 --> 28:33.950
but I still want to give it a try.

28:34.710 --> 28:35.510
Okay.

28:35.750 --> 28:36.950
You're an adult now.

28:37.150 --> 28:38.560
We respect your choice.

29:21.270 --> 29:22.230
Dinner is ready.

29:22.560 --> 29:23.080
Come on.

29:23.080 --> 29:23.990
Let's eat.

29:24.560 --> 29:26.120
The fish today is especially good.

29:26.990 --> 29:29.080
Ms. Liu, eat more.

29:29.080 --> 29:30.640
You've lost weight these past few days.

29:30.640 --> 29:32.700
Just eat your own food and don't worry about me.

29:32.850 --> 29:35.000
Right, Mrs. Shen. You should eat more,

29:35.030 --> 29:36.800
so your body can replenish its energy.

29:37.880 --> 29:39.030
Have some more fish.

29:39.030 --> 29:40.640
It's high in protein.

29:40.640 --> 29:42.400
Alright, alright, everyone just eat your own food.

29:42.400 --> 29:43.470
Don't worry about me.

29:43.470 --> 29:45.360
Here, let me check for bones.

29:46.470 --> 29:47.840
The fish today

29:47.990 --> 29:49.360
is steamed really well.

29:50.400 --> 29:52.780
I'll treat you all to a meal outside some other day.

29:53.250 --> 29:55.160
The restaurant's in a small alley by the lake,

29:55.230 --> 29:57.270
and its dishes are light in flavor overall.

29:57.270 --> 29:58.320
The fish there

29:58.510 --> 29:59.800
is incredibly tender.

30:00.510 --> 30:02.160
It's perfect for Ms. Liu to eat now.

30:02.240 --> 30:03.000
Yes.

30:03.510 --> 30:04.600
There are no bones. Go ahead and eat.

30:04.600 --> 30:07.270
How about I learn to cook too?

30:07.600 --> 30:08.670
I just quit my job,

30:08.670 --> 30:09.950
and I have nothing much to do at home.

30:09.950 --> 30:12.840
This way, I can let Ms. Liu try my cooking.

30:13.320 --> 30:14.880
That's a good idea.

30:14.880 --> 30:15.750
This way, when you go study abroad,

30:15.750 --> 30:17.350
you can cook for yourself.

30:22.130 --> 30:23.080
Speaking of studying abroad,

30:23.100 --> 30:25.870
Shen, how's your visa application going?

30:27.430 --> 30:29.920
Suye said you're not leaving until October?

30:31.440 --> 30:32.120
Yes.

30:32.120 --> 30:33.360
I've already submitted my visa application.

30:33.360 --> 30:34.560
I'm waiting for the results now.

30:36.160 --> 30:37.470
Learning to cook is good.

30:37.740 --> 30:40.910
Foreign food doesn't satisfy Chinese appetites.

30:41.780 --> 30:43.020
Learn to cook while you can.

30:43.050 --> 30:44.420
It's a win-win situation.

30:46.190 --> 30:47.880
Right. When you are abroad,

30:47.880 --> 30:49.670
Mr. Shen and I won't be there to cook for you anymore.

30:50.080 --> 30:52.320
Are you just going to eat bread,

30:52.320 --> 30:53.510
sandwiches, and such?

30:54.120 --> 30:56.080
Alright, I'll start learning this week.

30:56.470 --> 30:58.430
If I don't learn well, I'll blame you.

31:00.870 --> 31:01.760
Okay.

31:02.750 --> 31:03.640
Have some soup first.

31:07.320 --> 31:08.190
Go ahead and eat.

31:09.990 --> 31:10.670
Is it too hot?

31:32.990 --> 31:33.750
Dr. He.

31:33.750 --> 31:35.230
Ms. Liu's test results are out.

31:35.230 --> 31:36.560
I'll have Gu Ping bring them down to you.

32:04.560 --> 32:05.320
Senior He.

32:05.800 --> 32:07.920
Here's Ms. Liu's pathology report.

32:08.950 --> 32:09.990
Okay, thank you.

32:23.750 --> 32:24.730
Luminal A (Type A breast cancer).

32:48.670 --> 32:49.470
He.

32:49.880 --> 32:53.230
The result of this pathology report should be considered good,

32:53.230 --> 32:53.920
right?

32:54.080 --> 32:54.840
Yes.

32:55.230 --> 32:57.270
Mrs. Shen, it's an early-stage tumor.

32:57.300 --> 32:59.120
And based on the molecular subtype,

32:59.120 --> 33:00.030
the prognosis is very good.

33:00.030 --> 33:00.910
There's no need to worry.

33:02.080 --> 33:02.840
Really?

33:02.840 --> 33:03.640
Yes.

33:05.950 --> 33:07.800
We've arranged two treatment plans for you.

33:07.990 --> 33:09.750
One is a 15-day radiotherapy course,

33:09.750 --> 33:11.460
and the other is endocrine therapy.

33:11.600 --> 33:12.920
For the 15-day radiotherapy,

33:12.920 --> 33:13.800
it's five times a week,

33:13.800 --> 33:15.120
for three consecutive weeks.

33:15.400 --> 33:17.710
The endocrine therapy will have a longer cycle,

33:17.710 --> 33:18.890
requiring five years.

33:19.840 --> 33:21.920
But the advantage of this treatment plan is

33:21.920 --> 33:22.800
you don't need to be hospitalized.

33:22.990 --> 33:25.080
You can go home to rest after each radiotherapy session.

33:26.360 --> 33:27.360
That would be great.

33:27.990 --> 33:28.950
I can just stay at home.

33:28.980 --> 33:29.420
Yes.

33:29.950 --> 33:31.490
With this treatment plan,

33:31.710 --> 33:32.670
I'm confident that

33:32.670 --> 33:33.880
the five-year survival rate

33:33.880 --> 33:35.670
can reach over 95%.

33:36.710 --> 33:38.190
So it's not 100%?

33:39.600 --> 33:40.640
There's no treatment plan

33:40.640 --> 33:42.190
that can guarantee 100% survival rate.

33:42.190 --> 33:43.360
95%

33:43.420 --> 33:44.770
is already very, very high.

33:49.950 --> 33:51.190
I understand. I understand.

33:51.510 --> 33:53.710
It's like a student taking an exam.

33:54.160 --> 33:56.120
Ms. Liu, in this big test of life,

33:56.120 --> 33:57.920
you've scored 95 points.

33:58.030 --> 34:00.230
It's very high, right, He?

34:00.230 --> 34:01.400
Exactly.

34:02.400 --> 34:03.580
It's very high.

34:06.360 --> 34:08.150
Mrs. Shen, during the treatment,

34:08.150 --> 34:10.469
there will inevitably be some adverse reactions and side effects.

34:10.590 --> 34:12.150
If you feel any discomfort,

34:12.150 --> 34:13.360
you must let me know.

34:13.590 --> 34:15.110
I can use TCM methods

34:15.110 --> 34:16.530
to help alleviate these side effects for you.

34:17.949 --> 34:18.719
I'll do as you say.

34:19.699 --> 34:21.530
Alright, we can relax now.

34:21.590 --> 34:22.679
We have He here to take care of things.

34:26.010 --> 34:26.860
It's okay now.

34:28.900 --> 34:30.230
It was really frightening.

34:31.840 --> 34:33.699
Alright. We can feel at ease now.

34:38.550 --> 34:39.469
He.

34:46.150 --> 34:46.800
He.

34:47.030 --> 34:47.550
Mrs. Shen.

34:48.760 --> 34:50.550
I'll take you to the radiotherapy clinic.

34:50.840 --> 34:53.670
The doctor might ask you about your medical history,

34:53.800 --> 34:54.469
perform a physical examination,

34:54.469 --> 34:55.110
and review your previous

34:55.110 --> 34:56.510
CT scan reports and such.

34:56.510 --> 34:57.680
You just need to sign,

34:57.800 --> 34:59.200
and then we can start the radiotherapy.

35:00.800 --> 35:01.550
Which way?

35:01.550 --> 35:02.400
It's just ahead.

35:03.150 --> 35:04.360
Don't worry, it'll be fine.

35:05.990 --> 35:06.620
Let's go.

35:27.250 --> 35:28.320
Come on, Mom.

35:29.290 --> 35:29.920
Thank you.

35:29.990 --> 35:30.590
Have a seat.

35:31.360 --> 35:32.720
Do you feel unwell anywhere?

35:33.110 --> 35:34.470
I'm okay. I just want some water.

35:34.470 --> 35:35.280
You want water?

35:35.660 --> 35:36.780
Sit down. I'll get it.

35:43.200 --> 35:44.030
Drink slowly.

35:57.110 --> 35:57.870
It's okay.

36:06.760 --> 36:07.840
Don't worry.

36:49.390 --> 36:50.100
Hello.

36:51.180 --> 36:51.790
Are you

36:51.810 --> 36:53.730
Ms. Shen from Room 1201?

36:53.880 --> 36:54.760
Yes, that's me.

36:55.500 --> 36:57.460
There's a package from the embassy for you.

36:57.550 --> 36:58.880
If you're home, open the door,

36:58.920 --> 36:59.720
and I'll bring it up to you.

37:00.550 --> 37:01.470
Sure, no problem.

37:01.470 --> 37:02.470
I'll come right over.

37:02.500 --> 37:03.310
Okay.

37:17.170 --> 37:19.600
[Switzerland Visa Application Center]

38:16.160 --> 38:17.640
How is it? I did a good job, right?

38:17.670 --> 38:18.820
I made three dishes.

38:22.110 --> 38:23.360
Isn't it a bit bland?

38:23.360 --> 38:24.360
Add some more salt.

38:24.510 --> 38:25.630
We shouldn't add more salt.

38:25.660 --> 38:27.510
Ms. Liu needs to eat lighter food recently.

38:28.030 --> 38:29.200
But this is too bland.

38:29.200 --> 38:30.280
And they're all vegetarian dishes.

38:30.950 --> 38:32.670
What, are you eating all vegetarian dishes too after you go abroad?

38:34.630 --> 38:36.920
It's okay. I'll teach you a few meat dishes this weekend.

38:37.200 --> 38:38.680
Let's talk about it this weekend then.

38:38.680 --> 38:39.630
How can we postpone it...

38:39.630 --> 38:40.460
By the way,

38:40.600 --> 38:42.760
my dad's made a few extra dishes tonight.

38:42.780 --> 38:44.050
Let's go home for dinner tonight.

38:44.280 --> 38:44.800
Okay.

38:45.200 --> 38:46.160
I'll tidy up a bit first.

38:46.400 --> 38:47.150
I'll go wash my hands.

38:47.150 --> 38:47.720
Alright.

39:11.000 --> 39:14.340
[Switzerland Embassy]

40:34.400 --> 40:35.630
Let me get you some more soup.

40:36.200 --> 40:37.070
I can't eat anymore.

40:37.910 --> 40:39.060
Come on, have a little more.

40:39.080 --> 40:40.390
I worked hard to make this.

40:41.880 --> 40:42.590
Okay?

40:43.760 --> 40:44.670
Just one spoonful.

40:45.300 --> 40:46.170
One spoonful it is then.

40:47.030 --> 40:47.970
One spoonful.

40:53.030 --> 40:53.880
Eat slowly.

40:55.630 --> 40:56.920
How's the taste? Is it okay?

41:01.590 --> 41:02.200
It's delicious.
